  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: Wow, is that a red dragon scale in your hand?
    nextOption: Yes, I was going to ask you about it
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'And you defeated a dragon to get it?


      And you are still alive?'
    nextOption: Where did that thing come from anyway?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Sorry about that, I forgot the ATM was still configured to dispense
      those.


      However, you have earned the respect of the dragon by defeating it.


      You can now ride it any time you want.'
    nextOption: And it won't bite me?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: No, dragons are very honorable and will serve anyone who can best
      them for life.
    nextOption: So how do I call it?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Wrap your hands around the scale, and use it as a whistle.


      Dragons can hear the whistle created by their own scales from anywhere.'
    nextOption: Thanks, I'll try it now!
